name: Pappasang - Erwin Sulaiman
description: Pappasang (wasiat / advice) is the basic element in this instrumental music. Where the flute / bamboo flute is the main instrument. His general tone / notation was adopted & developed into a sound that is quite fresh for an ethnic-based instrumental. The main goal, so that ethnic music can be preserved. This ability can be seen by adapting it with several instruments and chords to use instrumental music that is quite interesting.
